  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mindbytes: Learn to Read Music is the most fun way to learn the how to read musical notation.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250020/extras/051043d246cb8d5f189bd554ddddf9b4.avif?t=1674418047\" width=630 height=130 /></span><br><br>• Learn each note on both the treble and bass clefs<br>• Learn what various musical notation symbols mean<br>• Click the notes to learn how they sound<br>• Think fast and challenge yourself to reach the highest score in the fast-paced and fun game mode<br>• Clicking the correct note earns you time, but getting the wrong answer causes a time penalty<br>• Get as many correct answers as possible before time runs out<br>• Reference flash-cards to look up any notes you haven't memorised yet",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Mindbytes: Learn to Read Music is the most fun way to learn the how to read musical notation.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250020/extras/051043d246cb8d5f189bd554ddddf9b4.avif?t=1674418047\" width=630 height=130 /></span><br><br>• Learn each note on both the treble and bass clefs<br>• Learn what various musical notation symbols mean<br>• Click the notes to learn how they sound<br>• Think fast and challenge yourself to reach the highest score in the fast-paced and fun game mode<br>• Clicking the correct note earns you time, but getting the wrong answer causes a time penalty<br>• Get as many correct answers as possible before time runs out<br>• Reference flash-cards to look up any notes you haven't memorised yet",
